## SUCCESS METRICS

**Visual Design:**
- All components use semantic classes from design system
- Color tokens used consistently (no inline colors)
- Spacing follows design scale
- Dark mode colors verified

**Accessibility:**
- WCAG AA compliance (contrast >= 4.5:1)
- Keyboard navigation works on all pages
- Touch targets >= 44px × 44px
- Screen reader compatible

**Responsiveness:**
- No horizontal scrolling on mobile (375px)
- Proper layout reflow at breakpoints
- Touch-friendly on all device sizes
- Performance acceptable (CLS < 0.1)

**Code Quality:**
- CSS organized by token → component → layout
- DRY principle applied (no duplication)
- Test coverage comprehensive
- HTML validates against standards

